verbose_text: As an alternative approach to solve the discrepancy, we have tried to use anatase as an internal standard during the Rietveld refinement, effectively fixing the anatase contribution to 63.75 wt% (= 75 wt% (the amount of anatase in titania) of 85 wt% (the amount of titania in the catalyst according to the impregnation for a 15 wt% Co/TiO 2 catalyst)).
